Duma Ka Ndlovu’s Ukhozi FM interview on the afternoon drive show with Tshatha Ngobe and Selbeyonce was very inspiring and impressive indeed! After being honoured with a doctorate from the University of Zululand, formerly Ongoye University,  Ka Ndlovu narrated that during his youth days growing up in Soweto he always wanted to attend Ongoye University but financial difficulties at home wouldn’t let him! Siyakubongela Gatsheni!  For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.